java.lang.Object
  reck.trees.RECKParseTreeImpl

java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, RECKParseTree
public class RECKParseTreeImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements RECKParseTree, java.lang.Cloneable, java.io.Serializable

A class representing a complex structure of a sentence. It contains a constituent, a dependency parse tree with the position in the sentence.
